aces%20no%20serious%20threat%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bany%20significant%20switch%20will%20take%20a%20long%20time%20to%20evolve%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDollar%20assets'%20unmatched%20liquidity%20and%20the%20private%20sector's%20heavy%20reliance%20on%20the%20greenback%20will%20support%20it%20over%20the%20longer%20term%2C%20according%20to%20the%20German%20financial%20services%20giant.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20movement%20among%20nations%20from%20China%20to%20Argentina%20to%20challenge%20the%20dollar's%20dominance%20of%20global%20trade%20and%20investment%20flows%20has%20attracted%20much%20attention%20of%20late.%20But%20the%20greenback's%20status%20as%20the%20world's%20reserve%20currency%20faces%20no%20real%20threat%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%20according%20to%20Allianz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20currency's%20supremacy%20is%20cemented%20by%20the%20private%20sector's%20heavy%20reliance%20on%20it%20for%20transactions%2C%20and%20an%20unmatched%20supply%20of%20safe%20and%20liquid%20dollar-denominated%20assets%20that's%20available%20for%20global%20central%20banks%20to%20invest%20their%20reserves%20in%2C%20the%20German%20insurance-to-asset%20management%20giant%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20has%20been%20made%20of%20a%20rival%20currency%20one%20day%20usurping%20%26quot%3BKing%20Dollar%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%93%20with%20Beijing%20pushing%20for%20more%20yuan-based%20trade%2C%20the%20BRICS%20countries%20planning%20a%20currency%20backed%20by%20gold%2C%20and%20Argentina%20using%20the%20Chinese%20currency%20for%20bank%20accounts%20and%20making%20debt%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20any%20significant%20change%20to%20the%20dollar's%20reign%20%26quot%3Bwill%20take%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Allianz%20economists%20led%20by%20Ludovic%20Subran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20dynamics%20affecting%20the%20US%20dollar's%20role%20as%20reserve%20currency%20are%20far%20more%20intricate%20than%20official%20statistics%20suggest%20and%20any%20material%20decline%20in%20the%20role%20of%20the%20US%20dollar%20in%20global%20finance%20will%20take%20much%20longer%20than%20current%20headline%20news%20on%20de-dollarization%20insinuate%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20private%20sector's%20use%20of%20the%20US%20dollar%20for%20trade%20and%20investment%20rather%20than%20the%20portfolio%20allocation%20choice%20of%20central%20banks%20will%20shape%20the%20currency's%20status%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20greenback's%20role%20in%20private-sector%20transactions%20has%20remained%20virtually%20unchanged%2C%20with%20only%20slight%20adjustments%20based%20on%20foreign-exchange%20turnover%2C%20bond%20issuance%20by%20non-financial%20corporates%20and%20SWIFT%20payments%2C%20according%20to%20Allianz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20addition%2C%20reserves%20are%20predominantly%20invested%20in%20safe%20and%20liquid%20assets%2C%20but%20the%20non-US%20dollar%20investment%20universe%20remains%20too%20small%20and%20fragmented%20to%20absorb%20reserves%20demand%2C%20especially%20in%20those%20EM%20countries%20that%20have%20been%20most%20critical%20of%20their%20US%20dollar%20dependence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20economists%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dollar%20still%20makes%20up%20almost%2060%25%20of%20all%20global%20reserves%20%E2%80%93%20while%20China's%20yuan%20accounts%20for%20just%203%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund.%20It's%20also%20the%20currency%20with%20which%20crude%20oil%2C%20natural%20gas%20and%20other%20key%20commodities%20are%20traded%20%E2%80%93%20facilitating%20contracts%20for%20countries%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-global-forex-reserves-dollar-brics-russia-china-yuan-allianz-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689246333000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3