is%20a%20significant%20rise%20from%20the%2016%20that%20had%20gathered%20at%20Patna%20on%20June%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20of%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20headed%20by%20Jayanat%20Choudhary%2C%20which%20had%20skipped%20the%20Patna%20meet%20has%20confirmed%20its%20participation%20for%20the%20Bengaluru%20one.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20which%20had%20attended%20the%20Patna%20meet%20but%20had%20skipped%20the%20press%20conference%20will%20attend%20the%20Bengaluru%20meeting%20as%20well%2C%20according%20to%20leaders%20of%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20in%20Patna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20yet%20assured%20the%20AAP%20of%20its%20support%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government%E2%80%99s%20ordinance%20nullifying%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20to%20give%20the%20Delhi%20government%20larger%20control%20over%20the%20bureaucracy%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Calmost%20convinced%E2%80%9D%20his%20Delhi%20counterpart%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrategists%20working%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20said%20that%20the%20Bengaluru%20meet%20might%20see%20the%20formation%20of%20three%20working%20groups%20which%20will%20draft%20a%20common%20agenda%20for%20opposition%20parties%20with%20the%20polls%20in%20mind.%20The%20meet%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20decide%20upon%20a%20common%20name%20for%20the%20opposition%20alliance.%20The%20parties%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20discuss%20tricky%20seat%20sharing%20arrangements%20among%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20parties%20which%20are%20likely%20to%20attend%20the%20meet%20are%20the%20Revolutionary%20Socialist%20Party%2C%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%2C%20Kerala%20Congress%20(M)%2C%20Viduthalai%20Chiruthaigal%20Katchi%2C%20Marumalarchi%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%2C%20Kerala%20Congress%20(J)%20and%20Forward%20Bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20parties%20which%20are%20scheduled%20to%20attend%20the%20July%2017-18%20meet%20share%20150%20MPs%20among%20themselves%20in%20the%20current%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20is%20likely%20to%20host%20a%20dinner%20for%20opposition%20party%20leaders%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20meet%20on%20July%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20will%20crystallise%20how%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20national%20party%20in%20the%20opposition%20%E2%80%93%20sees%20its%20own%20role%20in%20solidifying%20the%20anti-BJP%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fpolitics%2Fpatna-amidst-aap-congress-sparring-16-opposition-parties-vow-to-unitedly-fight-the-bjp%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3E16%20Parties%20Vow%20to%20Unitedly%20Fight%20the%20BJP%2C%20Hark%20Back%20to%20Patna%E2%80%99s%20Historic%20Role%20in%20Opposition%20Unity%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETop%20four%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exercise%20to%20unite%20opposition%20parties%2C%20which%20began%20about%2011%20months%20ago%2C%20has%20witnessed%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20the%20stature%20of%20four%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20party%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20boss%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%E2%80%99s%20role%20assumes%20importance%20considering%20the%20open%20secret%20that%20his%20Bengal%20counterpart%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20that%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20too%20is%20uncomfortable%20with%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Nitish%20has%20made%20efforts%20to%20get%20these%20two%20parties%20with%20conflicting%20interests%20in%20respective%20states%20to%20join%20the%20common%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20outdone%20his%20own%20reputation%20in%20displaying%20extraordinary%20political%20acumen%20in%20dealing%20with%20tricky%20situations%20within%20his%20own%20party%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-shows-his-mettle-and-guile-in-parliament%5C%22%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%20Shows%20His%20Mettle%20and%20Guile%20in%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20brought%20victory%20for%20his%20party%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20then%20sorted%20out%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20Karnataka%20CM%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20his%20deputy%20D.K.%20Shivakumar.%20He%20has%2C%20ostensibly%2C%20worked%20to%20maintain%20a%20delicate%20balance%20between%20the%20Rajasthan%20CM%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20his%20rival%20Sachin%20Pilot%2C%20and%20done%20the%20same%20between%20Chhattisgarh%20CM%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20his%20rival%20turned%20deputy%20T.%20S.%20Singh%20Deo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20losing%20his%20MP%20role%20following%20his%20conviction%20in%20a%20defamation%20case%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20continuous%20machinations%20against%20him%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20has%20made%20efforts%20in%20connecting%20with%20the%20masses%2C%20particularly%20agriculturists.%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20draws%20comparisons%20with%20his%20grandmother%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20photographs%20showing%20him%20with%20the%20farm%20workers%20in%20muddy%20fields%20must%20add%20to%20the%20discomfiture%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20who%20often%20draws%20flak%20for%20his%20ostentation%20and%20extravagance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20was%20in%20jail%20for%20over%20four%20years%20ever%20since%202017.%20He%20underwent%20a%20kidney%20transplant%20after%20he%20procured%20bail.%20But%20when%20he%20participated%20in%20a%20political%20activity%20at%20Patna%20on%20June%2023%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20last%20six%20years%2C%20he%20stole%20the%20show%20with%20the%20assertion%20%E2%80%93%20in%20his%20inimitable%20style%20%E2%80%93%20that%20he%20would%20%E2%80%98fix%E2%80%99%20Modi.%20He%20made%20the%20audience%20laugh%20with%20his%20characteristic%20light%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%20BJP%20Gears%20Up%20for%202024%20Polls%2C%20Thrust%20Will%20Be%20on%20Modi%20as%20Statesman%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-2024-polls-narendra-modi-statesman%5C%22%3EAs%20BJP%20Gears%20Up%20for%202024%20Polls%2C%20Thrust%20Will%20Be%20on%20Modi%20as%20Statesman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20BJP%20has%20stepped%20up%20using%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20and%20huge%20financial%20resources%20at%20its%20command%20is%20visible%20in%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20several%20of%20his%20colleagues%20in%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20joining%20its%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Pawar%20and%20four%20others%20had%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20hot%20on%20their%20heels%20in%20connection%20with%20cases%20of%20scams%20and%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20current%20CM%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%2040%20MLAs%20had%20defected%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20to%20form%20a%20BJP%20supported%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Goa%20and%20several%20other%20northeast%20states%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20succeeded%20in%20engineering%20large%20scale%20defections%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20to%20replace%20the%20elected%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20also%20constantly%20tried%20to%20split%20the%20JD(U)%20in%20Bihar.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-bihar-central-agencies-ajit-pawar-tejashwi-nitish%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3Eit%20has%20failed%