ws-in-12-days-4203490%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22I'd%20Rather%20Die%20Than%20Return%5C%22%3A%20Pak%20Woman%20Who%20Crossed%20Over%20For%20Indian%20Man%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20love-struck%20couple%20from%20arch-rivals%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20who%20met%20in%20a%20gaming%20chatroom%20before%20sneaking%20across%20borders%20to%20be%20together%2C%20say%20their%20passion%20trumped%20national%20rivalries%20or%20fear%20of%20religious%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%20Meena%2C%2022%2C%20an%20unmarried%20Indian%20shopkeeping%20assistant%20and%20a%20Hindu%2C%20connected%20with%2027-year-old%20Seema%20Haider%2C%20a%20married%20Pakistani%20mother%20of%20four%20and%20a%20Muslim%2C%20playing%20the%20online%20shooting%20game%20PUBG%20during%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20became%20friends%20and%20our%20friendship%20turned%20to%20love%20and%20our%20chats%20became%20longer%20--%20every%20morning%20and%20night%20--%20before%20we%20finally%20decided%20to%20meet%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Seema%2C%20speaking%20to%20AFP%20from%20the%20cramped%20courtyard%20of%20Sachin's%20two-room%20family%20home%2C%20where%20she%20now%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%2C%20who%20left%20Pakistan%20and%20her%20husband%20with%20her%20four%20children%20by%20smuggling%20herself%20into%20India%20via%20Nepal%20in%20May%20--%20for%20which%20the%20couple%20were%20arrested%20then%20bailed%20out%20last%20week%20--%20said%20she%20has%20since%20married%20Sachin%20and%20taken%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20converted%20to%20Hinduism%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20sitting%20next%20to%20Sachin%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Rabupura%2C%20about%2055%20kilometres%20(35%20miles)%20from%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20rather%20die%20than%20return%20or%20leave%20Sachin%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20lovers%20have%20found%20each%20other%2C%20the%20history%20of%20their%20respective%20nations%20is%20bitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20both%20nuclear-armed%20nations%2C%20have%20fought%20three%20wars%20since%20being%20carved%20out%20of%20the%20subcontinent%20in%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20expelled%20the%20other's%20high%20commissioner%20in%202019%2C%20and%20bilateral%20diplomatic%2C%20cultural%2C%20business%20and%20sporting%20links%20are%20very%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20police%20insist%20that%20Seema's%20long-term%20stay%20will%20be%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20request%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20grant%20me%20citizenship%26quot%3B%2C%20Seema%20pleaded%2C%20a%20red%20headscarf%20covering%20her%20hair%20and%20her%20four%20young%20children%20playing%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Destined'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApostasy%20is%20considered%20punishable%20by%20death%20in%20some%20interpretations%20of%20Islam.%20Seema%20said%20she%20had%20already%20received%20online%20threats%20and%20insisted%20the%20couple%20would%20%26quot%3Blive%20and%20die%20together%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema's%20proclamation%20of%20%26quot%3Bundying%20love%26quot%3B%20for%20Sachin%20and%20a%20promise%20to%20only%20return%20to%20Pakistan%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20dead%20woman%26quot%3B%20when%20they%20featured%20on%20a%20raucous%20Indian%20TV%20debate%20this%20week%20drew%20cheers%20from%20the%20crowds%20sitting%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20said%20she%20had%20been%20first%20attracted%20by%20Sachin's%20gaming%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20the%20couple%20met%20in%20person%20in%20March%20in%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20became%20sure%20about%20leaving%20her%20%26quot%3Babusive%26quot%3B%20Pakistani%20husband%20--%20charges%20he%20denies%20--%20after%20the%20first%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20said%20it%20took%20months%20of%20meticulous%20planning%20with%20help%20from%20YouTube%20videos%20on%20how%20to%20enter%20India%20via%20Nepal.%20In%20May%2C%20she%20succeeded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20travel%20from%20Pakistan%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20with%20God's%20love%2C%20we%20were%20destined%20to%20meet%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin's%20family%20only%20learned%20of%20her%20existence%20when%20he%20rented%20a%20nearby%20apartment%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20some%20resistance%2C%20but%20my%20father%20and%20everyone%20accepted%20us.%20They%20are%20happy%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sachin.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20do%20everything%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20police%20found%20out%20after%20they%20tried%20to%20get%20married%20at%20a%20local%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Still%20my%20family'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema's%20estranged%20husband%2C%20Ghulam%20Haider%2C%20left%20his%20job%20as%20a%20labourer%20and%20rickshaw%20driver%20to%20earn%20more%20money%20for%20his%20family%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaider%2C%20who%20said%20he%20had%20not%20heard%20of%20PUBG%2C%20wants%20his%20family%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20earnestly%20appeal%20to%20Indian%20and%20Pakistani%20authorities%20to%20bring%20my%20wife%20and%20children%20back%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghulam%20Haider%20told%20AFP%20by%20phone%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaider%20said%20the%20couple%2C%20from%20different%20Baloch%20tribes%2C%20have%20a%20defiant%20love%20story%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForbidden%20by%20their%20families%20from%20marrying%2C%20they%20ran%20away%20to%20get%20hitched%20--%20a%20taboo%20in%20Pakistan%20that%20can%20sometimes%20lead%20to%20so-called%20honour%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLater%2C%20a%20jirga%20(council%20of%20elders)%20was%20summoned%20to%20settle%20the%20matter%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20one%20million%20rupees%20(around%20%243%2C640)%20was%20slapped%20on%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said