49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESAG-AFTRA%20members%20joined%20the%20writers'%20picket%20line%20at%20Netflix%20headquarters%20in%20LA%20on%20Tuesday.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20midnight%20deadline%20for%20a%20new%20contract%20between%20actors%20and%20major%20studios%20passed%20without%20agreement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESAG-AFTRA's%20negotiating%20board%20voted%20unanimously%20to%20recommend%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20could%20be%20the%20first%20simultaneous%20strike%20by%20actors%20and%20writers%20in%20more%20than%2060%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20representing%20160%2C000%20actors%20is%20set%20to%20call%20for%20a%20strike%20after%20contract%20talks%20failed%20to%20reach%20an%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20be%20the%20first%20time%20in%2043%20years%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sagaftra.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESAG-AFTRA%3C%2Fa%3E%20members%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-hollywood-actors-writers-strike-could-end-nightmare-scenario%5C%22%3Estop%20working%20on%20TV%20and%20film%20productions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20not%20since%201960%20have%20both%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-writers-strike-over-technology-ai-netflix-streaming-studios-2023-7%5C%22%3Eactors%20and%20writers'%20unions%20taken%20industrial%20action%20at%20the%20same%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20midnight%20deadline%20for%20a%20new%20contract%20with%20the%20Alliance%20of%20Motion%20Picture%20and%20Television%20Producers%20(AMPTP)%20%E2%80%93%20which%20represents%20major%20studios%20and%20streaming%20services%20including%20Warner%20Bros%2C%20Disney%2C%20and%20Netflix%20%E2%80%94%20passed%20without%20an%20agreement%20after%20four%20weeks%20of%20bargaining%2C%20SAG-AFTRA%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel