ern%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20embassy%20in%20London%20called%20the%20accusation%20%26quot%3Bdisinformation%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20the%20US%20government%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world's%20biggest%20hacking%20empire%20and%20global%20cyber%20thief.%26quot%3B%20China%20routinely%20denies%20involvement%20in%20hacking%20operations%20regardless%20of%20the%20available%20evidence%20or%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20Adam%20Hodge%20said%20an%20intrusion%20in%20Microsoft's%20cloud%20security%20%26quot%3Baffected%20unclassified%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20without%20elaborating%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOfficials%20immediately%20contacted%20Microsoft%20to%20find%20the%20source%20and%20vulnerability%20in%20their%20cloud%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hodge%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department%20%26quot%3Bdetected%20anomalous%20activity%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btook%20immediate%20steps%20to%20secure%20our%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20department%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20Commerce%20Department%20said%20it%20took%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20action%26quot%3B%20after%20Microsoft%20notified%20it%20of%20a%20compromise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20sector%20cybersecurity%20experts%20have%20said%20newly%20discovered%20hacking%20activity%20shows%20how%20Chinese%20groups%20are%20improving%20their%20cyber%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChinese%20cyber%20espionage%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20from%20the%20smash-and-grab%20tactics%20many%20of%20us%20are%20familiar%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Hultquist%2C%20chief%20analyst%20for%20U.S.%20cybersecurity%20firm%20Mandiant.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689243840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fvo1fk6sg_hacker-generic-getty_625x300_16_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-hackers-breached-us-government