31300199e7cc6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22596%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShriya%20Boppana%3Cp%3EShriya%20Boppana%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20took%20the%20job%20because%20they%20paid%20the%20most%2C%20but%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Texas%2C%20it%20was%20the%20biggest%20financial%20drain%20on%20my%20bank%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20barely%20even%20enjoyed%20the%20perks%20of%20a%20fat%20paycheck.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoppana%20said%20her%20company%20initially%20required%20her%20to%20move%20for%20the%20job%2C%20but%20after%20two%20months%2C%20she%20was%20allowed%20to%20move%20back%20home%20to%20Virginia%20and%20work%20remotely.%20After%20paying%20rent%20for%20another%20six%20months%2C%20she%20said%20she%20flew%20back%20to%20Austin%20to%20break%20her%20lease%2C%20pick%20up%20her%20car%2C%20and%20drive%2022%20hours%20back%20to%20Virginia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20can%20sometimes%20mean%20giving%20up%20lifestyle%20preferences%2C%20like%20being%20car-free%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJulianne%20Elise%2C%2025%2C%20told%20Insider%20she%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20her%20New%20York%20City%20public%20relations%20manager%20job%20in%20June.%20Two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20she%20said%20she%20received%20a%20job%20offer%20for%20a%20role%20that%20paid%20slightly%20more%20than%20her%20old%20gig%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20company%20said%20she'd%20have%20to%20move%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221128%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julianne%20Elise%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ad9f638ed31300199e7c52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22846%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulianne%20Elise%3Cp%3EJulianne%20Elise%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20said%20she'd%20be%20open%20to%20moving%20for%20a%20new%20job%2C%20she%20ultimately%20decided%20to%20decline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20on%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20realized%20that%20I%20would%20need%20a%20car%2C%20which%20is%20an%20added%20expense%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20rent%20in%20LA%20was%20slightly%20lower%20than%20I'm%20paying%20in%20New%20York%2C%20but%20not%20enough%20to%20justify%20buying%20a%20car%20and%20the%20moving%20expenses%20I%20would%20incur.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh%20housing%20costs%20can%20make%20a%20good%20job%20offer%20less%20attractive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAngela%20Harris%2C%2043%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20she%20moved%20from%20Philadelphia%20to%20Redmond%2C%20Washington%20in%202019%20for%20a%20new%20job.%20She%20said%20she'd%20lived%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%20her%20entire%20life%20and%20was%20looking%20for%20something%20new.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20was%20fortunate%20that%20her%20new%20employer%20covered%20most%20of%20her%20relocation%20expenses%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20temporary%20stay%20in%20corporate%20housing%20%E2%80%94%20she%20said%20she%20found%20herself%20losing%20money%20elsewhere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Angela%20Harris%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ada19a8ed31300199e7cf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22528%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAngela%20Harris%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Philadelphia%2C%20she%20said%20she%20had%20a%20%241%2C200%20monthly%20mortgage%20payment%20for%20a%203-bedroom%20home.%20But%20in%20Redmond%2C%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20rent%20a%202-bedroom%20home%20for%20%242%2C400%20per%20month.%20She%20also%20said%20her%20car%20registration%20was%20%24500%20the%20first%20year%2C%20up%20drastically%20from%20the%20%2440%20annual%20payment%20she'd%20become%20accustomed%20to%20in%20Pennsylvania.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20living%20expenses%20doubled%2C%2