3E%2C%20the%20complaint%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20Kuki%20Students%20Organisation%20(KSO)%20on%20June%2013%20but%20the%20case%20was%20registered%20only%20on%20July%208%20at%20the%20Kangpokpi%20police%20station.%20The%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20invokes%20charges%20such%20as%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups%2C%20intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20peace%20and%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20filed%20by%20the%20KSO%20mentions%20statements%20made%20by%20Singh%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-meitei-leepun-pramot-singh-karan-thapar-manipur-violence-kukis%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20June%206.%20Statements%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9CKukis%20are%20outsiders%20who%20are%20not%20indigenous%20to%20Manipur%E2%80%9D%20have%20been%20cited%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20also%20notes%20that%20Singh%20accepted%20that%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20was%20training%20people%20to%20use%20arms%20and%20warned%20that%20there%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20a%20civil%20war%20and%20the%20Kukis%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20defend%20themselves%E2%80%9D.%20The%20complaint%20also%20cited%20tweets%20that%20Singh%20or%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20had%20posted%2C%20which%20it%20says%20instigated%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeitei%20Leepun%20and%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20have%20been%20accused%20by%20Kuki%20groups%20of%20instigating%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20groups%20deny%20this%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20FIR%20and%20that%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20bothered%E2%80%9D%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20have%20been%20ongoing%20since%20May%203%2C%20have%