that%20wildlife%20veterinarian%20was%20a%20thing.%20I%20would%20watch%20people%20on%20NatGeo%20on%20rescue%20missions%20and%20it%20would%20always%20thrill%20me.%20I%20was%20always%20looking%20for%20the%20right%20opportunity%20which%20I%20got%20recently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20degree%2C%20she%20joined%20a%20rescue%20company%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20started%20working%20as%20a%20veterinarian.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202022%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Mangaluru%20with%20my%20husband%20who%20had%20a%20clinic%20there.%20He%20was%20helping%20out%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20forest%20department%2C%20which%20gave%20me%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20get%20into%20onfield%20rescuing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20nearly%20two%20years%20since%20Meghana%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F122995%2Ffed-delays-26-year-old-creates-app-helps-rescue-animals-real-time%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erescuing%20wild%20animals.%3C%2Fa%3E%20She%20has%20assisted%20the%20forest%20department%20on%20several%20missions%20and%20has%20rescued%20eight%20leopards%2C%20bringing%20them%20home%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJumping%20in%20wells%20%26amp%3B%20climbing%20building%20is%20a%20routine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20duty%20call%20for%2024%20hours%2C%20it%20is%20the%20passion%20for%20wildlife%20that%20keeps%20the%20veterinarian%20going.%20She%20has%20been%20in%20rescue%20missions%20which%20entail%20risks%20for%20both%20her%20and%20the%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20go%20on%20a%20mission%2C%20the%20animal%20is%20always%20my%20top%20priority.%20Leopards%20are%20frequently%20the%20ones%20we%20rescue%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20they%20are%20just%20as%20afraid%20of%20us%20as%20we%20are%20of%20them.%20There%20are%20significant%20risks%20of%20injury%20for%20both%20myself%20