0call%20it%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20own%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ekarma%20while%20others%20say%20it%20is%20Keshubhai%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20curse%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20in%202012%2C%20Modi%20found%20himself%20isolated.%20Even%20the%20RSS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Frss-pulls-up-modi-for-forcing-gadkaris-hand%2Farticle3484272.ece%5C%22%3Eorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPanchjanya%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20hit%20out%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98style%20of%20functioning%E2%80%99%20as%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPitted%20against%20Modi%20were%20an%20array%20of%20Gujarat%20seniors%20like%20former%20chief%20minister%20Suresh%20Mehta%2C%20Kashiram%20Rana%2C%20Gordhan%20Zadaphia%2C%20Nalin%20Bhat%2C%20Sidharth%20Parmar%20and%20Pravin%20Maniar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAging%20and%20ailing%2C%20Keshubhai%20Patel%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fkeshubhai-patel-continues-his-tirade-against-narendra-modi%2Farticleshow%2F15034271.cms%5C%22%3Ecursed%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20old%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echela%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20called%20him%20a%20%E2%80%98rhino%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0He%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Easked%20people%20to%20guard%20against%20the%20antics%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia%2Fkeshubhai-cautions-people-against-modi-praises-joshi%2Fstory-2urOlZBEl6mxaGZIBD5TSJ.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elanpot%20sankh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(a%20Gujarati%20term%20for%20braggart)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fwest%2Fstory%2Fnarendra-modi-is-a-demon-says-keshubhai-patel-110986-2012-07-24%5C%22%3Edescribed