%20a%20front%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20an%20extremely%20serious%20allegation%20levelled%20by%20a%20chief%20minister.%20He%20has%20challenged%20the%20very%20personal%20integrity%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister.%20Modi%20had%20in%20the%20past%20charged%20the%20UPA%20government%20with%20a%20series%20of%20scams.%20But%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20accused%20Manmohan%20Singh%20of%20personal%20involvement.%20In%20fact%2C%20no%20prime%20minister%20in%20India%20was%20ever%20accused%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20direct%20personal%20involvement%20in%20any%20such%20misdemeanours%2C%20not%20even%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20enriching%20his%20friends%20but%20not%20himself.%20This%20renders%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20the%20Adani%20imbroglio%20even%20more%20surprising.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F07213949%2FScreenshot-2023-02-07-at-9.38.38-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F07213949%2FScreenshot-2023-02-07-at-9.38.38-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F07213949%2FScreenshot-2023-02-07-at-9.38.38-PM-300x152.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F07213949%2FScreenshot-2023-02-07-at-9.38.38-PM-1024x520.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-639529%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22609%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20holds%20up%20a%20photo%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20a%20private%20jet%20with%20Gautam%20Adani%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20February%207%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20via%20Sansad%20TV%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBlame%20it%20on%20the%20stars%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekarma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20dawn%20of%202023%20found%20Modi%20totally%20tongue-tied%20on%20half%20a%20dozen%20pressing%20issues.%20For%20several%20months%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20champion%20wrestlers%20were%20on%20the%20streets%20seeking%20action%20against%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20president%2C%20Brijbhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20also%20a%20BJP%20MP.%20Women%20wrestlers%2C%20including%20minors%2C%20alleged%20repeated%20sexual%20misbehaviour%20by%20Singh%2C%20who%20had%20for%20years%20established%20a%20vice-like%20grip%20on%20the%20entire%20federation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECrucial%20positions%20in%20the%20WFI%20are%20held%20by%20his%20kin%20and%20friends%20who%20controlled%20the%20entire%20outfit.%20As%20the%20agitation%20and%20dharna%20continued%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%2C%20Modi%20and%20his%20ministers%20were%20busy%20breaking%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20protesters.%20While%20Singh%20was%20gaily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdetained-wrestlers-supporters-angry-at-bjp-mp-brij-bhushan-singh-attending-parliament-inaugural%5C%22%3Erubbing%20shoulders%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20party%20bosses%20at%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%2C%20the%20police%20were%20manhandling%20the%20wrestlers%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20detained%20and%20kept%20in%20the%20police%20station%20for%20hours%20before%20finally%20being%20charged%20with%20rioting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20one%20stage%2C%20the%20wrestlers%20were%20so%20disheartened%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20break%20his%20silence%20that%20they%20went%20to%20Hardwar%20to%20throw%20their%20medals%20into%20the%20Ganga.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20persuaded%20not%20to%20do%20so%20by%20leaders%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions.%20The%20wrestlers%20also%20got%20widespread%20support%20from%20the%20middle%20classes%20and%20youth.%20A%20C-Voter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Findia-news%2Fmost-indians-want-brij-bhushan-arrested-expect-pm-modi-to-intervene-survey%2F3115464%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2068.4%25%20of%20the%20people%20interviewed%20wanted%20the%20PM%20to%20take%20strong%20action%20against%20the%20accused%20BJP%20MP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhap%20panchayats%20extended%20full%20support%20to%20the%20wrestlers%20and%20organised%20their%20own%20protests.%20Women%20from%20the%20mahapanchayat%20rushed%20to%20Delhi%20to%20join%20the%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20dharna.%20None%20of%20this%20moved%20Modi%20who%2C%20as%20a%20diehard%20despot%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewent%20by%20his%20own%20cold%20calculations.%20Jat%20votes%2C%20which%20can%20influence%2040%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20spread%20over%20four%20states%2C%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fbjp-jat-community-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-lok-sabha-seats-8655513%2F%5C%22%3Eimportant%20for%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20ignoring%20the%20Brijbhushan%20factor%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbrij-bhushan-gonda-raj-over-50-colleges-schools-hospitals-hotel-8656158%5C%22%3Ealso%20be%20politically%20fatal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20this%20dilemma%20that%20forced%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cstrongest%20prime%20minister%E2%80%9D%20into%20a%20long%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emaunvrat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20break%20the%20agitation.%20He%20deputed%20Anurag%20Thakur%2C%20who%20sought%20to%20wean%20away