nt.%20He%20has%20no%20voice%2C%20he%20has%20no%20mouth%2C%20he%20has%20no%20spine%20to%20carry%20on%20the%20responsibility%2C%20so%20we%20are%20coming%20together%20today%20as%20ZORO%20in%20Aizawl%20to%20be%20in%20solidarity%20with%20our%20suffering%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20in%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERalter%20said%20that%20they%20are%20only%20demanding%20their%20due%20right%20to%20have%20a%20separate%20administration%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20Meitei%20community%20do%20not%20want%20the%20tribals%20anymore.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20point%20of%20coming%20together%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20them%20anymore%3F%20This%20is%20the%20only%20option%20they%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ralte%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20effigy%20was%20marked%20with%20a%20tape%20on%20his%20lips%20to%20display%20his%20alleged%20silence%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20as%20the%20ZORO%20condemned%20the%20silence%20over%20the%20issue.%20The%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20effigy%20was%20given%20the%20title%20%E2%80%9CMafia%20Godfather%E2%80%9D.%20An%20official%20said%20that%20the%20burning%20of%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20effigy%20was%20a%20display%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20deserves%20to%20die%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20effigy%20lit%20up%2C%20the%20crowd%20went%20into%20a%20fury%20shouting%20curses%20in%20Manipuri%20language%20against%20the%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20burning%20effigies%2C%20a%20mass%20prayer%20was%20conducted%20where%20all%20the%20people%20who%20gathered%2C%20shouted%20and%20cried%20in%20unison%20for%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20Amid%20a%20solemn%20atmosphere%2C%20a%20mourning%20session%20commenced%2C%20with%20the%20ringing%20of%20a%20gong%2C%20evoking%20ancient%20traditions%20and%20conveying%20messages%20of%20sorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20protestors%20were%20displaced%20residents%20of%20Manipur.%20Among%20them%20was%20a%20college%20student%20Lalremruat%20Tonsing%20from%20L