ally%20high.%20They%20rushed%20her%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20walk%20a%20few%20steps%20without%20panting%20at%20that%20time.%20I%20was%20very%20unhealthy.%20When%20my%20parents%20had%20to%20take%20care%20of%20me%20in%20their%2060s%2C%20I%20decided%20that%20enough%20was%20enough.%20That%20was%20the%20first%20turning%20point%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrash%20diets%20had%20not%20worked%20for%20Aathira%20because%20in%20her%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98Food%20is%20life!%E2%80%99%20So%20the%20only%20way%20forward%2C%20she%20realised%2C%20was%20to%20look%20for%20a%20sustainable%20diet.%20So%20while%20she%20was%20home%20alone%20for%20a%20week%20after%20the%20incident%20at%20her%20sister%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20she%20started%20researching%20nutrition%20and%20made%20a%20few%20tweaks%20to%20her%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAathira%2C%20who%20weighed%20100%20kg%20at%20the%20time%2C%20lost%20three%20kilos%20in%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20526px)%20100vw%2C%20526px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faathiraa-1688628921.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20recent%20picture%20of%20Aathira%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faathiraa-1688628921.jpeg%20526w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faathiraa-1688628921-154x300.jpeg%20154w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faathiraa-1688628921-500x973.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faathiraa-1688628921-150x292.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-322871%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAathira%20believes%20that%20portion%20control%20and%20calorie%20deficit%20works%20for%20weight%20loss%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%20lost%20weight%20in%20a%20very%20visible%20manner.%20I%20finally%20realised%20that%20this%20was%20possible%2C%20so%20I%20started%20taking%20it%20seriously.%20I%20did%20in-depth%20research%20into%20nutrition.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20give%20up%20on%20things%20I%20liked%20to%20eat.%20And%20the%20easiest%20way%20I%20found%20is%20to%20cook%20at%20home%20and%20make%20healthier%20versions%20of%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Aathira.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306747%2Fkirti-yadav-kukclean-bengaluru-offers-plant-based-vegan-sugar-free-healthy-snacks-for-diabetes-patients%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20continued%20her%20workouts%20and%20now%20enjoyed%20them.%20She%20focused%20on%20strength%20training%20and%20intense%20cardio%2C%20and%20walked%2010%2C000%20steps%20daily.%20She%20even%20hired%20a%20personal%20trainer%20at%20the%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20four%20months%2C%20she%20lost%2020%20kg%2C%20and%20because%20of%20this%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20stop%20taking%20her%20cholesterol%20and%20blood%20pressure%20medications.%20She%20went%20from%20having%20periods%20once%20every%20four%20months%20to%20experiencing%20them%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis%2C%20with%20a%20cycle%20of%2030%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20more%20months%20after%20that%2C%20her%20weight%20reduced%20to%2074%20kg%2C%20and%20she%20also%20saw%20positive%20changes%20in%20her%20strength%2C%20immunity%20and%20overall%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20about%20myself.%20Growing%20up%20as%20a%20fat%20kid%2C%20I%20had%20never%20taken%20an%20interest%20in%20physical%20education.%20But%20now%2C%20I%20figured%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20total%20%E2%80